**Bitcoin Classifieds** features free online classified advertisements for goods and services where the seller accepts bitcoins. It was created to make it easier for people to get in contact with each other and trade services and goods using Bitcoins.

The site was announced April 3rd, 2011 (1.1)

If you have any suggestions or tips to make the website better, you can contact the webmaster here:
[Contact](http://www.bitcoinclassifieds.net/Contact/)

